-- Poland Adopts New Energy Policy Sought for PGE's Takeover of Rival Energa
-- B y   M a r t a   W a l d o c h   a n d   M a c i e j   M a r t e w i c z
-- 2010-09-29T11:01:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/poland-adopts-new-energy-policy-sought-for-pge-s-takeover-of-rival-energa.html
 Poland’s government approved a
policy change intended to speed up a deal accounting for 30
percent of planned asset-sale revenue this year, it said in a
statement.  The government said it supports PGE SA’s 7.5 billion-zloty
aquisition of Energa SA and the takeover is needed to build the
country’s nuclear power plant, the statement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marta Waldoch at 
